column5: Hi All, Heading up to Parry Sound for holidays; last year around this time i found an auction that was selling off a lot of random stuff but LOTS of boats and motors. Are any of you familiar with this auction???  I was hoping to catch it again this year but havent seen anything advertised.  Any help is appreciated.  Adam
If you do find it .. I'd be very interested too ... thanks in advance  for sharing.
